Veteran  musician, Zaaki Azzay has explained why he returned to the four walls of the university to secure another degree. In an exclusive chat with The Nation, the famous singer said one of his motivations for returning to school was to eradicate bad leadership in the country.   Kizz Daniel secures double deal     Nkechi Blessing, husband fight dirty amid breakup     Someone gave me N3m for being a good girl – Ese Eriata   “I went back to school to find out for myself the nemesis or source of bad leadership that has constantly been the major setback of Nigeria as a country and also to avail myself for service if I must change the situation,” he told The Nation. The singer noted that this was why he opted for political science as the course will help him provide good leadership while availing himself of service. “My reason for choosing to read political science is to provide good leadership to my country Nigeria against all odds,” he said.